To install hardest, download and unpack the tarball where you want
the installation (do e.g. "tar -xzf hardest.1.5.tar.gz"). 

Then run "make -s". If you want a different compiler or
mode than the defaults, then, instead of "make -s", use e.g.
"make gccrelease" or "make -s -f makefile_icc_release_static".

(Do a "make install" if you want to install the program wider.)
